        "id": "day1_consultation08-091",
        "speaker": "Doctor",
        "start": 328.998,
        "end": 338.372,
        "text": "Uh , the reason I ask is sometimes stress can be a , contributing factor. Um, you felt, you noticed yourself, find, uh, , life's been more stressful recently. Is that right?"
