        "id": "day1_consultation08-096",
        "speaker": "Doctor",
        "start": 360.258,
        "end": 374.812,
        "text": "Um, it's difficult. I think that, you know, , you've, essentially the story is you've got a dry itchy rash on your, mainly your hands. you mentioned. Um and your arms which started, perhaps after swimming a few days ago."
