        "id": "day1_consultation08-106",
        "speaker": "Doctor",
        "start": 424.497,
        "end": 432.23,
        "text": "Um, , you can also try antihistamines, so you can get things over the counter, Piriton, Loratadine, they can sometimes help with the itchiness."
