        "id": "day1_consultation09-097",
        "speaker": "Doctor",
        "start": 482.797,
        "end": 493.109,
        "text": "Yeah, yeah absolutely. And things to look out for would be, you know, if you are having kind of, high temperatures, a back pain, um just , generally feeling more unwell."
