        "id": "day1_consultation11-131",
        "speaker": "Doctor",
        "start": 736.592,
        "end": 745.399,
        "text": "Because um, you know if you are getting dehydrated then we need to do further investigations, OK? But I think let's, let's see how you are in the next one to two days."
