        "speaker": "Patient",
        "start": 748.381,
        "end": 758.168,
        "text": "OK. So you're saying that I should, I could, uh I'll try and buy this Dioralyte. What, what should I do in terms of um, food and that kind of thing? Should I just focus on fluids?"
