        "id": "day2_consultation01-033",
        "speaker": "Doctor",
        "start": 134.753,
        "end": 143.766,
        "text": "No, OK. Well, you're right, you should, you shouldn't be doing that. Doesn't clean up wax, it pushes it back in. Alright, um, the first thing that we need to do is we need to get someone to have a look inside your ear."
