        "id": "day2_consultation04-090",
        "speaker": "Doctor",
        "start": 364.502,
        "end": 375.278,
        "text": "OK. Last thing, is if I can get you to feel inside your neck. Just on the sides here, OK, um, by your Adam's apple. Tell me whether you can feel any enlarged glands or not."
