        "id": "day3_consultation09-060",
        "speaker": "Patient",
        "start": 335.134,
        "end": 342.822,
        "text": "Uh, and, but that, that just lasted not very long. I mean, that just lasted maybe for, I don't know, twenty, twenty minutes?"
