        "id": "day3_consultation10-095",
        "speaker": "Doctor",
        "start": 455.191,
        "end": 471.036,
        "text": "Yeah? So, um, at the same time you could have some, although you can't milk is not a good idea, yoghurts are a good idea because they are probiotics, it help to build up the normal, um gut, gut bacteria back."
