        "speaker": "Patient",
        "start": 440.911,
        "end": 452.784,
        "text": "Uh, well, but I never had it, and I thought that the onset of migraine will be, you know, in much, uh, early ages. So, that's why I'm not sure, if migraine makes sense. ."
