        "id": "day5_consultation08-032",
        "speaker": "Doctor",
        "start": 128.246,
        "end": 138.067,
        "text": "OK. And when do you think it last, when do you think that asthma stopped? At what age did you get to a point where you weren't taking medication anymore?"
