        "id": "day5_consultation08-035",
        "speaker": "Doctor",
        "start": 148.462,
        "end": 158.358,
        "text": "And so this time, how did it start? Did you have any other symptoms? Any chest pain, temperature, cold symptoms, anything like that?"
