        "id": "day5_consultation11-101",
        "speaker": "Doctor",
        "start": 525.224,
        "end": 535.558,
        "text": ". And, what I would suggest is, definitely carrying on with the ice therapy that you've been using. So, as much as you can, 'cause that really does make a difference to injuries."
