        "id": "day5_consultation11-111",
        "speaker": "Doctor",
        "start": 584.71,
        "end": 593.94,
        "text": "And then we can make an assessment as to whether we need to do any, um, imagery to , have a look inside the knee, and see if there's any problem with the, cartilage."
